[3] Pakistan (Sindh province)
Date: Tue 24 Apr 2018
Source: Daily Times [edited]
https://dailytimes.com.pk/231715/three-children-die-of-measles/


At least 3 children lost their lives on [Mon 23 Apr 2018] due to fresh measles outbreak.

Reportedly, a 3-year-old and 4-year-old died in Bozdar wada village [Sindh] while another child died in Channer village.

The villagers claimed that at least 6 children died while others are suffering.

They demanded health department to appoint doctors in their village for the treatment.

